verse = \lyricmode {
  Let them not say, \"Yes, we have won.
We've swal -- lowed him; he is un -- done!\"
Those who a -- gainst me are as -- sem -- bled
be shamed, by their con -- fu -- sion hum -- bled,
and let all vic -- to͜ry be de -- nied
to those puffed up with boast -- ing pride.
Let all who gloat at my ex -- pense
be clothed with shame as rec -- om -- pense.
}
